# Array.take/drop — Interactive Diff from List

Reference: `List.take`/`List.drop` lemmas (multiple files)
Target: `src/Init/Data/Array/TakeDrop.lean` (currently empty)

Naming conventions: `length` → `size`, `[]`/`nil` → `#[]`/`empty`, `l` → `xs`

Note: `Array.take`/`Array.drop` are defined in terms of `Array.extract`:
- `Array.take xs i = xs.extract 0 i`
- `Array.drop xs i = xs.extract i xs.size`

Existing Array lemmas: `take_eq_extract`, `drop_eq_extract`, `toList_take`, `toList_drop`,
`shrink_eq_take`, `take_toArray`, `List.drop_toArray` (in `Array.Lemmas`).

